Voyager New Moves

Muddy Terrain

Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
5 0 Weaken ballistics, boost ground, prioritize Mud moves.

Details

-Weakens ballistic moves (ball/bomb moves)

-Increases the priority of 'Mud' moves (mud slap, mud sport, muddy water, mud shot, and mud bomb)

-Muddy Water's power increased by 50%

-Increases ground-move power by 30%
